problem: Is double duty an incorrect phrase for host of Dancing With The Stars?
gt_solution:
Double duty refers to having more than one job at the same time.
The host of Dancing WIth The Stars is Tom Bergeron.
Tom Bergeron is the host of America's Funniest Home Videos.
facts: Double duty refers to having more than one job at the same time.
